<p style="font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; color: red;">DEADLINES - Payment for tuition is always due <strong>10 days before class begins.</strong>&nbsp;  We then give up until one week after the first day of school to make changes in your classes.  The payment deadline is 7 days after school starts.  At this time if you do not have your tuition paid you will have a 5% late fee assessed to your tuition and insurance account.<br />Also, if you drop classes after the payment deadline date you will not receive a refund on your tuition.  The only way to get a refund is if you were to withdraw from the semester and at that time we will give you a prorated refund.</p>
